description:
Mandatory masks got you pissed off?
I don't know about you, but not seeing anyone else stand up for their rights really pisses me off.
There can be mass protests and riots and everything's fine?
Now that they are over, everything is scary again?
Tell them to go fuck themselves with that crap.
Grab yours today, I'm wearing mine right now.
